Dozen Nigerien Farmers Are Murdered by Armed Group in Mali, Minister Says

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-06-21T09:58:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/dozen-nigerien-farmers-are-murdered-by-armed-group-in-mali-minister-says.html
As many as 12 Nigerien farmers were
killed and another seven injured by a group of armed men in the
Tuareg region of  Mali , Abdou Labo, Niger’s minister of the
interior, said in an interview broadcast on national radio.  “The attackers arrived on motorcycles equipped with
weapons,” he said on Niamey-based Voix du Sahel today. “They
killed a dozen farmers.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  